items.title: feat(INT-18857): Create App Tile | Step 2 - Tile Builder (Save, Publish & Cancel)
items.body:
[Link to Jira](https://simpplr.atlassian.net/browse/INT-18857)

Description goes here
- Added save and publish functionality to Tile Builder step
- Removed unused TilePreview stepper component as preview is included in Tile Builder
- Added {cacheTime: 0} for getTileDetails api, to refetch data for any changes done in TileBuilder schema, otherwise it was showing cached data before if we were saving ,going back to tile list screen and coming back to TileBuilder again
- Handle case when a tile is already published (not showing publish again and not putting operationType:"publish" in api call, showing different toast message)




https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e7cf0ebb-dacd-467d-986c-448bb1ecdc2a
